latestPosts.caption:
The Panel: Kickstart Gender Equality through Sports for Development had discussions ranging from
understanding how Sports for Development Approach help in bridging the gender and creating
spaces and avenues for girls to navigate public spaces and also how it capacitates the girls to have
leadership and livelihood skills which help them when it comes to employability. The panel also
discussed the realities and challenges of the girls and organizations working in Sports.
Thanks to our Moderator and Speakers -
Suheil F Tandon from @prosportdevelopment
@sha_o_na
@naino04 from @yuwaindia
@malaa_4131 
You can check out the full conversation on our YouTube channel or click the link in the bio!
https://www.youtube.com/live/mydPryW9QgQ?si=bFaw5-9ffHXlRR6K
